# Project Scope Statement  
**Project:** [Project Name]  
**Version:** 1.0  
**Last Updated:** [Date]

## In Scope
- [Bullet list of deliverables/features in this phase, e.g.]
  - Agent skill system with progressive loading
  - Modular planning docs
  - Git + artifact organization rules
  - Support for PHP/Python/Next.js stacks

## Out of Scope (for this phase)
- [What is explicitly NOT included, e.g.]
  - Full CI/CD pipeline implementation
  - Mobile deployment scripts
  - Paid third-party API integrations
  - GUI for skill management

## Assumptions
- Agent has access to Antigravity/Claude Code/Cursor
- Models support 32k+ context window

## Constraints
- Keep active context <25k tokens
- Prefer open-source tools

## Acceptance Criteria
- All core features work end-to-end
- Agents follow yes/no loop and silent execution
- Artifacts saved correctly

